\begin_layout Enumerate
Review process: (
\begin_inset Formula $\sim60$
\end_inset

 minutes)
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Students should enter the workshop with an example of their work on the
 topic of choice.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Randomized pairs can exchange their individual papers to 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

neighbouring
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 pairs, and each pair can discuss amongst themselves about how their peers'
 papers can be improved (by using the rubric provided by faculty).
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
Working in pairs encourages discussion, and is hence potentially more beneficial
 than working as individuals.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Itemize
