 by going from pair to pair and giving their input, or just be around to
 answer questions that the pair may have.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
Coffee break (15--30 minutes, depending on how long/short the review process
 is)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Post discussion (
\begin_inset Formula $\sim20$
\end_inset

 minutes, depending on how chatty the group is)
\end_layout

